node.text:
How many courses are sitting in your course graveyard? 🪦

Lemme guess, it was a white guy, talking at a whiteboard showing you the 458495 simple steps you need to take to set up your bazillion dollar funnel? 😜

Now listen, I LOVE a funnel as much as the next guy, but if things are over-complicated (or, over-boring 😬) I just can’t seem to focus, let alone implement. 

And so there we go again, throwing money into the course graveyard and telling ourselves we’ll never do it again…

Enter: The Société… the NEW, sleek, fun way to do things.

Listen, we were SO done with all the complicated, boring online programs and memberships…

That’s why we rolled up our sleeves, loaded up on espresso and got to work creating the most incredible corner of the internet for ambitious women, just like you.

Here’s the thing: without the right mindset, accountability and dare I say it - FUN, the information your brain is overloaded with never seems to turn into anything material.

...(I mean, if it did, we’d watch a few TikToks and call it a six figure day).

Inside The Société, unlike other memberships, we combine results-driven education (from actual real-deal 7, 8 and 9 figure serial entrepreneurs) WITH built in accountability to help you get the best results for your business.

Hit the link in our bio to sign up for THE membership for ambitious women, and we’ll see you on the inside. ⬆️

node.title: Start or Scale Your Business With The Société

node.text:
From 0 followers to household name, here’s exactly what I did: ⬇️

Let’s first bust two myths you might’ve heard floating around:

Myth #1: Building a successful business is easy…

Myth #2: There’s one single thing you can do to become successful…

Firstly, it isn’t easy - it’s more like a roller coaster that you get on daily.  🎢

But it is seriously worth it. Kinda the same as ANYTHING worth having right?

Secondly, there isn’t one secret funnel or social media trick that is going to turn your idea into a successful business overnight…

However, there is a step-by-step process that almost any business type, in any industry, can follow. This process will take you from the baby idea stage, to having an incredibly successful, 6, 7 or 8+ figure business.

Me and my business partner, Danielle, created this process after a combined decade in multiple businesses, and after mentoring over 120,000 students ourselves.

We realized that there are six steps that you can follow in a linear fashion, to create a successful business. Think of it as your Satellite Navigation (Tesla style) to profit. 💸

So, we took these steps and built an entire membership platform around them, to take the guesswork out of the process. We call it: The Société.

Right now, doors are open to The Société and members who join us right now (for less than the cost of a latte per day!) are going to get access to a bundle of bonuses on top of their membership.

Ready to stop driving in circles and plug into a system that actually works? Hit the link in our bio below to join us!

node.text:
Real influence is built through sharing UNIQUE content.

That’s why we created The Content Masterclass...to teach you how to STAND OUT so you don’t end up just fitting in.

This is perfect for you if…

✅ You’re ready for a brand new content strategy and want to learn exactly how you can use your own uniqueness to truly build influence and stand out.

✅ You don’t know WHAT content to post never mind HOW to create it, and want to get more intentional and purposeful with what you put out online

✅ You’re camera shy, and want to learn how to increase your confidence so you’re much more comfortable in front of it

✅ You want a feed that’s aesthetically pleasing like other entrepreneurs' and influencers' online, where the fonts and colours are consistent and visually reflect you and your business/brand but don’t know where to start

✅ You post from time-to-time but when you do, it’s to crickets - you want to learn the kind of content that’s actually going to get you engagement and increase your reach

✅ You don’t have any fancy equipment, but you do have a smartphone, and want to learn how to use it to capture photos and videos that look legit

✅ You’re in a permanent state of post paralysis because you don’t have a bank of content to pull from - you want to learn how to batch so you can create quickly, easily and always have plenty of choice

✅ You want to learn how to edit like a pro, so that you can elevate your content and uplevel your feed so it looks not just cute, but cohesive too

...because in this course, I’ll be spilling ALL of our content creation and marketing secrets, and you can access it this weekend ONLY for $97 instead of $500 (saving 80%!). 🤯

Click our link in bio to sign up at the discounted price before our sale ends on Monday at midnight!

node.title: Real influence doesn’t come from cookie cutter captions and content.

node.text:
Social media is changing. 

The kind of content that used to get engagement, a.k.a. likes, comments, shares and saves just isn’t hitting the mark anymore. 🤷‍♀️

The algorithm is giving favor to what keeps people on the platform…

...which means static images are out, and moving video like Reels and IGTVs are in.

But… that’s not the kind of content that’s super easy to produce if you’re not a professional, right?

And so you’ve probably noticed a huge drop in your engagement recently...

...but not to worry.

With 2.8M+ on Instagram, 232K+ on Facebook, 1.3M+ monthly views on Pinterest and 1M+ views on YouTube I think it’s safe to say that at BossBabe we know what works and what doesn’t when it comes to content creation and marketing, and we have a crazy amazing deal on a course, through which we teach you all we know. 😉

In The Content Masterclass, you'll get: 
📸7x modules of 16x videos designed with your content creation game in mind 
📸@iamnatalie's favorite presets for a professional finish in post-production 
📸BossBabe’s content calendar so you know EXACTLY what to post and when to attract an audience and drive traffic to make sales 
📸An exclusive video on how to monetize your content and grow your Instagram account 

Did we mention that all of this is $97 THIS WEEKEND ONLY?! That's right...over $2,600 worth of content for just $97.  What are you waiting for?! Link in bio!

node.text:
We’re so excited to have @goodamerican CEO and Co-founder, Emma Grede @emmagrede 👑, join us on the BossBabe Instagram to share the real behind-the-scenes of creating such a meaningful brand that truly promotes inclusivity and diversity beyond their campaigns.⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Emma is lifting the lid on what it took to build a multi-million dollar fashion brand in an already “saturated” denim industry. 💸⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
If you dream of having your own product-based business, then you’re in luck. Emma is delivering PURE value with mindset shifts and tangible actions that you can start implementing right away! 🙌⁣⁣⁣
⁣
🎙 Make sure to tune in to Emma's episode on #TheBossBabePodcast. Search for "The BossBabe Podcast Episode 98" on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, or anywhere you listen to podcasts.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣

node.title: How To Break Into a Saturated Market w/ Emma Grede, CEO of Good American

node.text:
It’s LAUNCH DAY! 🎉✨ Today, we launched Online Launch School: a 12-week program designed to take the guesswork out of online launches, whether you’re looking to start a business or scale one.⁣
⁣
Online Launch School is for you if you’re ready to have the biggest cash injection in your business that you’ve ever had, through learning how to launch effectively.⁣
⁣
This is our second course at BossBabe and if you were part of our first (IGA), you’ll know that we’re queens of overdelivering. That’s exactly what we’re bringing you this time around, too.⁣
⁣
If you join us within the next 14 days, here’s what bonuses you’re going to get:⁣
⁣
➡️ You’ll save $1,000 OFF your enrollment cost!⁣
➡️ Full access to Online Launch School (content valued at $4,997!)⁣
➡️ Bonus FB community with me, Danielle, team BossBabe & your OLS classmates, incl 6 x Q&A calls & a chance to get featured on BossBabe IG ($3,000 value)⁣
➡️ Done for you launch success planner ($97 value)⁣
➡️ 1 x free ticket to the BossBabe Online Launch Summit in October (virtual!) ($497 value)⁣
⁣
and the BEST bonus of all:⁣
⁣
➡️ Done for you funnel & copy bundle… aka pages of email sequence copy ready for you to plug and play, as well as ClickFunnels templates already designed for you. This comes with video tutorials, so even if you’ve never seen a funnel before, you’ll be able to implement with ease. This bundle alone is valued at $1497!⁣
⁣
All of this is valued at $10,088, but if you join us within the next 14 days, you’ll get full access for $997. ⚡️ Who’s in already?! We’re SO excited! Link in bio to join OLS now. ✨⁣
⁣
Or you can sign up for OLS here: https://bossbabe.com/join-ols⁣
⁣
Watch the webinar replay here: https://bossbabe.com/the-launch-formula⁣
⁣
Use code BOSSBABE to get 15% off your next purchase with @organifi: bossbabe.online/organifi

node.text:
[NEW PODCAST EPISODE 🎙️] Do you want to know the one thing that BossBabe’s co-founders, @iamnatalie and @daniellecanty, credit to the success of their business relationship? One word: communication.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Join us in this episode on The BossBabe Podcast as we take you behind-the-scenes of what it really looks like to be in a business relationship with your best friend and how to cultivate a thriving partnership.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
We'll cover:⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
✔️ How Natalie and Danielle use communication to cultivate a thriving business relationship⁣⁣⁣
✔️ The real behind-the-scenes of being Biz Besties while living and working together ⁣⁣⁣⁣
✔️ How Natalie and Danielle navigated being business partners from different parts of the world ⁣⁣⁣⁣
✔️ How things have changed since Danielle’s big move to join Natalie in Los Angeles⁣⁣⁣
✔️ Why over-communication is key, especially for remote teams based in different locations⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
🎙️To hear the full episode, search for "The BossBabe Podcast" on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, or anywhere you listen to podcasts.⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
#bossbabe #thebossbabepodcast #thebossbabesociete #bossbabe #sponsored

node.text:
NEW PODCAST EPISODE 🎤  What if we told you one of the things that contributes THE most to your overall health is actually…your gut.⁠
⁠
Seriously.⁠
⁠
But taking care of your gut + what that has to do with other parts of your health (think: mental health, skin clarity + immune system) can feel really elusive and confusing. ⁠
⁠
So this week, we invited Tina Anderson, CEO + founder of @justthrivehealth, to the podcast to unpack exactly what you can start doing today to take better care of your whole self – starting with your gut.⁠
⁠
If you’ve been looking to take better care of yourself and prioritize your health, but aren’t sure where to start – this is the episode you need to kickstart your journey to true self-care.⁠
⁠
Listen now!

Exercising might be hard, but never moving makes life harder. Uncomfortable conversations are hard, but avoiding every conflict is harder. Mastering your craft is hard, but having no skills is harder. Easy has a cost.'.

node.text: Life gets easier when you go the “harder” route.
